<div class="com-share" data-id="13453" data-title="《便利店都有什么好，日本人那么爱它？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/13453/medium/13453.jpg?1439440727" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/13453.html?url_type=39&amp;object_type=webpage&amp;pos=1" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
